{"title":"大漠的早晨","authors":["张满隆"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":5,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张满隆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，在天空的洗衣机里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行了一夜的搅动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗去了月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗去了星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把沉淀在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁滩的墨迹洗净。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始在驼铃上苏醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开一串串惺忪的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白桦林，拉开威武的队列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夹道欢迎黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳，又备足了火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备对大漠进行新的蒸腾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨风，送给坎儿井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片欢跳的灵感，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿洲，交给炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔缠绵的诗情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚从夜色中爬出的公路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动地驮来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一车车绿汪汪的青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和比青春更蓬勃的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和比歌声更动人的憧憬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面“支援西部”的大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画龙点睛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为大漠这幅油画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充实了最为生动的内容！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}